Interface Locatable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AdHocCommunicative, ChargingStationOperatingSystem, ElectricVehicleOperatingSystem, Navigable, RoadSideUnitOperatingSystem, TrafficLightOperatingSystem, VehicleOperatingSystem
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChargingStationUnit, ElectricVehicleUnit, RoadSideUnit, TrafficLightGroupUnit, VehicleUnit
    public interface Locatable
    Interface that marks a OperatingSystem as locatable, meaning that is located somewhere in world and is able to provide its location.
